class=\"Grid4\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/recruit/index.html\">採用情報トップページ</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/index.html\">新卒採用</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>先輩社員の声</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div><!-- /.breadcrumb-list -->\n\n\n\n\t<div class=\"GridSet\">\n\t\t<div class=\"Grid4\">\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-recruit sub-page-layout\" id=\"section-interview-top\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title-en is-vertical interview-top-vertical\">VOICE</div>\n\n                <div class=\"message-title\">\n                    <h1>EMPLOYEE'S<br>VOICE<span>先輩社員の声</span></h1>\n\t\t\t    </div><!-- /title-message -->\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /#section-interview-top -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-recruit\" id=\"section-interview-patt02\">\n                <div class=\"about-people-set\">\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/01.html\">\n                        <!--p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>クレーン設計部 クレーン設計グループ</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Yutaka.E<span>2013年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">メンテナンスのしやすさや操作性へのこだわり。<br>お客さまのニーズに合わせたクレーンの設計に全力で取り組んでいます。</p-->\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>クレーン設計部 クレーン設計グループ</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Noritaka.S<span>2019年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">お客様のニーズに寄り添い、安全を最優先に考えたクレーンの設計に<br>全力で取り組んでいます。</p-->\n                        </p></div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/02.html\">\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>品質保証部 品質保証課</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Yudai.A<span>2025年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">お客様の現場で迷惑をかけることがないように、まずは工場内の検査業務をしっかり実施しています。</p>\n                        </div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/03.html\">\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>東日本クレーンサービス部 アフターサービス設計グループ</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Shunya.T<span>2018年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">お客さまのニーズに最適な提案を。<br>\n環境にも配慮し、持続可能な未来を創ることを大切にしています。</p>\n                        </div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/04.html\">\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>生産技術部 製作課</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_04.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Ren.U<span>2025年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">製作の大部分を占める製缶手配。<br>製造現場が滞ることのないよう、早め早めの手配を心がけています。</p>\n                        </div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/05.html\">\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>中日本営業部 関西支店</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_05.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Miho.Y<span>2024年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">見えない力で、社会を支える影の立役者。<br>日本のモノづくりに欠かせないクレーンで人々の暮らしを豊かにするお手伝いをしています。</p>\n                        </div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n\n                    <a class=\"about-people-set-item\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/06.html\">\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-title\"><span>西日本クレーンサービス部 西部サービスセンタ</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"about-people-set-image\"><img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/image/img_interview_06.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"about-people-set-absolute\">\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-title\">Haruki.M<span>2022年入社</span></p>\n                            <p class=\"about-people-set-absolute-text\">「電気」という見えないものを扱う仕事。<br>自他ともに身を守るため心を引き締めて業務に取組んでいます。</p>\n                        </div><!-- /.about-people-set-absolute -->\n                    </a><!-- /.about-people-set-item -->\n                </div><!-- /.about-people-set -->\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /.section-recruit -->\n\n\n<div class=\"section-recruit multiple\" id=\"section-entry\">\n<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/back_entry.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n<div class=\"entry-inner\">\n<div>\n<p>ENTRY</p>\n<p>エントリーはこちらから</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-link\">\n<p><a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/26/pc/search/corp113326/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\">2026卒エントリー<span class=\"entry-arrow\"></span></a></p>\n<p>2027卒エントリー（準備中）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-6\">\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\t\t</div><!--/Grid4-->\n\t</div><!--/GridSet-->\n</div><!--/Contents-->\n\n\n\n<div id=\"FooterArea\">\n\t<div class=\"Container Wide\">\n\n\t\t<a href=\"#top\" id=\"FooterPageTop\" aria-label=\"ページの先頭へ\"></a>\n\n\t\t<div id=\"Footer1\">\n\n\t\t\t<div id=\"HitachiTop\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.hitachi.co.jp/\">日立グループTOP</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div id=\"Footer1Menu\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/utility/termofuse/index.html\">サイトの利用条件</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/utility/privacy/index.html\">個人情報保護に関して</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div id=\"Copyright\">&copy; Hitachi Plant Mechanics Co., Ltd.<span>2007</span>. All rights reserved.</div>\n\n\t\t</div><!--/#Footer1-->\n\n\t</div><!--/.Container-->\n</div><!--/#FooterArea-->\n\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.hitachi-hpm.co.jp/recruit/newgraduate/interview/index.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T20:40:17.089Z"}